abstract_str: democratic sen. tick __segerblom__ is sponsoring the measure that would allow animal owners to get marijuana for their pet . __segerblom__ said he 's concerned that some animals might have adverse reactions , but ` you do n't know until you try , ' he said . according to __canna__ companion , the drug is able to help pets with joint pain , anxiety , digestive issues , end of life care , and neurological function .
